            I grew up in a small beach town - Santa Cruz, California. My retail career has given me the chance to live in several different states, eventually landing here in Minnesota (or Minne-sohhh-ta as my father-in-law would say)
          </div>

          <div class="d-block right-body-content-about-technical">
            Technical: </br>
            Currently, I am developing web apps utilizing Ruby on Rails, Wordpress, HTML CSS SCSS JS

          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="d-block cheveron-container">
          <i class="d-inline chevron"></i>
        </div>


        <div class="right-body-content-grid">

          <div class="row pictures-row">
